column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID,s.sourceType,s.class,s.subclass,p.clean,p.RA,p.DEC,p.psfMag_u,p.psfMag_g,p.psfMag_r,p.psfMag_i,p.psfMag_z,p.psfMagErr_u,p.psfMagErr_g,p.psfMagErr_r,p.psfMagErr_i,p.psfMagErr_z,s.z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN specObj As s ON s.bestObjID= x.objID JOIN photoObj As p ON p.ObjID= x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
